# AGENTS.md

This file provides guidance to agents when working with code in this repository.

## Architect Mode Specific Instructions

### Multi-Attempt Reasoning (REQUIRED)

- Multi-attempt reasoning is REQUIRED before finalizing any solution
- Question every assumption and inference, support with comprehensive reasoning
- Think of better solutions than the present one by combining strongest aspects
- Repeat the process refining and integrating different solutions until a strong solution is found
- Solutions must be refined through multiple iterations before presentation

### Memory Bank (MANDATORY)

- Memory Bank loading is MANDATORY for EVERY task
- Read ALL files in `.kilocode/rules/memory-bank/` before starting
- Include `[Memory Bank: Active]` or `[Memory Bank: Missing]` in response
